translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今回は特別、許す、お前も飲め
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This time, I'll make an exception. You can drink, too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「は、はいっ♪
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Y-Yes!♪

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: わーい、嬉しいな♪
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yay, I'm so happy♪

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふーふー、ふーふー……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Blow, blow... blow, blow...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょびっ……あちち……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just a little... ouch, hot...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「飲んだか？　飲んだな？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Did you drink it? You did, didn't you?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「がははは、ねーちゃんとお茶したぞー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahaha, I had tea with Nee-chan!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちょーっと待って下さい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-Wait just a moment!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 納得いきません！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I won't accept this!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あーん？　負け犬の遠吠えが聞こえるなー？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? I hear the howling of a loser, huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えへ、えへへ、ランス様ぁ……♪
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ehe, ehehe, Lord Rance...♪

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 偉そうにどっかーとベンチに座るランスの足下で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At the feet of Rance, who sat arrogantly on the bench,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 地面にぺたりんこと座るシィルは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seel sat flat on the ground,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふにゃふにゃ幸せそうだった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: looking soft and happy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっ、なんたること！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, what a thing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これどうあっても、わたくしの敗北だ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No matter how you look at it, this is my defeat!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐああああ！　悔しいー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Guaaaa! It's frustrating!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「がはははははははははは！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahahahahahaha!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いーい気分ー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I feel great!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、シィル、まだ飲んでるのか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, Seel, are you still drinking?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい、とってもいい茶葉なので、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, since it's very good tea leaves,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちびちび楽しもうかなって……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm thinking of savoring it little by little...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、もういい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, it's fine now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 茶がもったいないから後は俺が飲む
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's a waste of tea, so I'll drink the rest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっ、あーーーっ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, ahhh!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「茶を飲んだシィルは用済み、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seel, who drank the tea, is no longer needed,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はよお使いに戻れ、しっしっ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hurry back to your errands, shoo shoo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「クスン……なんでですかぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sniff... Why is that...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「むむむ……なにやら主旨が変わってきましたが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm... It seems the main point is changing,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 悔しすぎてこのままでは引き下がれませんぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's too frustrating to back down now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、本格的にナンパ対決と行くか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, shall we seriously do a pick-up contest?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、それでいい気分にはなれないのは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, I know that won't make me feel good,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 分かっているので、わたくしめと同じ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I want to lower my bitterness by making someone else,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敗北者を作ることで溜飲を下げたいです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a loser, just like me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……本当にお前俗っぽいな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...You really are a mundane person.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おっ、あんなところにリック将軍……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, there's General Rick over there...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……あいつにナンパさせるのは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Having him do the pick-up,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し面白そうだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: seems a little interesting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「わたくしも今、全く同じことを……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was just thinking the exact same thing...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふふふ、リック殿がふられて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, watching Lord Rick get rejected

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あわてふためく様はきっととても愉快ですよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and flustered will surely be very amusing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前、ほんとーに正直者だな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You really are an honest person.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だが面白そうだ、やらせよう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But it sounds fun, let's make him do it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えっ、僕がナンパ……ですか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh, me doing pick-up...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだ、総統命令だ、やれ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, it's an order from the commander, do it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「赤軍の将の勇猛さを見せて下さい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Show us the bravery of the Red Army's general.
Eh, um...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、あのぉ……お嬢さん……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Uh, um... young lady...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 僕とお茶など、その……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Would you perhaps... like to have tea with me...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 行って頂けませんか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Would you go with me?
